an class=\"hl-identifier\" style=\"color:#0055AA;\">a</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> </span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">[</span><span class=\"hl-number\" style=\"color:maroon;\">9</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\">, </span><span class=\"hl-number\" style=\"color:maroon;\">2</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\">, </span><span class=\"hl-number\" style=\"color:maroon;\">6</span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">]</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n			List内置了有很多方法，例如append()、pop()等等，这在后面会讲到。\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n			<b>注意：</b>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<ul>\r\n			<li style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n				1、List写在方括号之间，元素用逗号隔开。\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n				2、和字符串一样，list可以被索引和切片。\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n				3、List可以使用+操作符进行拼接。\r\n			</li>\r\n			<li style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n				4、List中的元素是可以改变的。\r\n			</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n		<hr />\r\n		<h2 style=\"font-size:1.8em;\">\r\n			Tuple（元组）\r\n		</h2>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n			元组（tuple）与列表类似，不同之处在于元组的元素不能修改。元组写在小括号&nbsp;<span class=\"marked\" style=\"background-color:#ECEAE6;font-weight:bold;font-family:SFMono-Regular, Consolas, &quot;\">()</span>&nbsp;里，元素之间用逗号隔开。\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n			元组中的元素类型也可以不相同：\r\n		</p>\r\n		<div class=\"example\" style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;margin:0px 0px 5px;padding:5px;color:#000000;background-color:#E5EECC;\">\r\n			<h2 class=\"example\" style=\"font-size:14.4px;color:#617F10;background-color:transparent;\">\r\n				实例\r\n			</h2>\r\n			<div class=\"example_code\" style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;margin:0px;padding:5px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-size:13.2px;font-family:Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;\">\r\n				<div class=\"hl-main\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span class=\"hl-comment\" style=\"color:#AA5500;\">#!/