">tuple</span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">[</span><span class=\"hl-number\" style=\"color:maroon;\">2</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\">:</span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">]</span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">)</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> </span><span class=\"hl-comment\" style=\"color:#AA5500;\"># 输出从第三个元素开始的所有元素</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> </span><span class=\"hl-identifier\" style=\"color:#0055AA;\">print</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> </span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">(</span><span class=\"hl-identifier\" style=\"color:#0055AA;\">tinytuple</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> * </span><span class=\"hl-number\" style=\"color:maroon;\">2</span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">)</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> </span><span class=\"hl-comment\" style=\"color:#AA5500;\"># 输出两次元组</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> </span><span class=\"hl-identifier\" style=\"color:#0055AA;\">print</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> </span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">(</span><span class=\"hl-identifier\" style=\"color:#0055AA;\">tuple</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> + </span><span class=\"hl-identifier\" style=\"color:#0055AA;\">tinytuple</span><span class=\"hl-brackets\" style=\"color:olive;\">)</span><span class=\"hl-code\" style=\"color:gray;\"> </span><span class=\"hl-comment\" style=\"color:#AA5500;\"># 连接元组</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n			以上实例输出结果：\r\n		</p>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\"><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">(</span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'abcd\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </spa