\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							创建一个字典。d 必须是一个序列 (key,value)元组。\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							<a href=\"http://www.runoob.com/python3/python-func-frozenset.html\" target=\"_blank\">frozenset(s)</a>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							转换为不可变集合\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							<a href=\"http://www.runoob.com/python3/python-func-chr.html\" target=\"_blank\">chr(x)</a>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							将一个整数转换为一个字符\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							<a href=\"http://www.runoob.com/python3/python-func-ord.html\" target=\"_blank\">ord(x)</a>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							将一个字符转换为它的整数值\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n				</tr>\r\n				<tr>\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							<a href=\"http://www.runoob.com/python3/python-func-hex.html\" target=\"_blank\">hex(x)</a>\r\n						</p>\r\n					</td>\r\n					<td style=\"border:1px solid #D4D4D4;font-size:13px;vertical-align:top;\">\r\n						<p style=\"font-family:&quot;\">\r\n							将一个整数转换为一个十六