or:#006666;\">4098</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">)</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">{</span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'sape\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">:</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"lit\" style=\"color:#006666;\">4139</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'jack\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">:</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"lit\" style=\"color:#006666;\">4098</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'guido\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">:</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"lit\" style=\"color:#006666;\">4127</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">}</span></pre>\r\n		<hr />\r\n		<h2 style=\"font-size:1.8em;\">\r\n			遍历技巧\r\n		</h2>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n			在字典中遍历时，关键字和对应的值可以使用 items() 方法同时解读出来：\r\n		</p>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\"><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> knights </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">=</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">{</span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'gallahad\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">:</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'the pure\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'robin\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">:</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'the brave\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">}</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\" style=\"color:#000088;\">for</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> k</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> v </span><span class=\"kwd\" style=\"color:#000088;\">in</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> knights</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">.</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\">items</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">():</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">...</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\" style=\"color:#000088;\">print</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">(</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\">k</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> v</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">)</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">...</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> gallahad the pure\r\nrobin the brave</span></pre>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n			在序列中遍历时，索引位置和对应值可以使用 enumerate() 函数同时得到：\r\n		</p>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\"><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\" style=\"color:#000088;\">for</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> i</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> v </span><span class=\"kwd\" style=\"color:#000088;\">in</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> enumerate</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">([</span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'tic\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'tac\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"str\" style=\"color:#008800;\">\'toe\'</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">]):</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">...</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"kwd\" style=\"color:#000088;\">print</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">(</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\">i</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">,</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> v</span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">)</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">...</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> </span><span class=\"lit\" style=\"color:#006666;\">0</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> tic </span><span class=\"lit\" style=\"color:#006666;\">1</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> tac </span><span class=\"lit\" style=\"color:#006666;\">2</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> toe</span></pre>\r\n		<p style=\"font-size:13px;\">\r\n			同时遍历两个或更多的序列，可以使用 zip() 组合：\r\n		</p>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint prettyprinted\"><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000;\"> questions </span><span class=\"pun\" style=\"color:#666600;\">=</span><span class=\"pln\" style=\"color:#000000